      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 14:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行今年第四次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-cuts-interest-rates-fourth-time-this-year-2024-12-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四宣布年内第四次降息，并表示在通胀接近目标且经济依然疲软的情况下，未来进一步宽松的政策仍敞开大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-cuts-interest-rates-fourth-time-this-year-2024-12-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 13:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
